1
00:01:32,100 --> 00:01:34,940
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:38,030
[Episode 28]

3
00:02:20,790 --> 00:02:23,030
I—your new Emperor—am standing here
before you.

4
00:02:23,030 --> 00:02:24,160
Why do you not kneel?

5
00:02:24,630 --> 00:02:25,190
Kneel!

6
00:02:26,190 --> 00:02:30,520
Long live Your Majesty!

7
00:03:25,310 --> 00:03:26,110
Who is there?

8
00:03:26,430 --> 00:03:26,870
Who?

9
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:29,100
I am the Emperor.

10
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:31,680
Who dares to laugh at me?

11
00:03:32,190 --> 00:03:34,390
You're nothing but a lowborn bastard—

12
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,400
the child of a lowly maid.

13
00:03:38,150 --> 00:03:40,750
And you think you're worthy of
calling me Mother?

14
00:03:40,750 --> 00:03:41,610
You're only fit

15
00:03:42,190 --> 00:03:44,390
to be trampled underfoot by Xiahou Dan!

16
00:03:44,870 --> 00:03:45,400
Beat him.

17
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:46,950
Beat him hard!

18
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:58,840
Bo!

19
00:03:59,870 --> 00:04:00,360
Bo!

20
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:01,590
Bo!

21
00:04:01,910 --> 00:04:02,360
Bo!

22
00:04:02,710 --> 00:04:03,150
Bo.

23
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,630
My poor Bo.

24
00:04:05,150 --> 00:04:06,080
Are you alright?

25
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:09,460
The child is innocent.

26
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:12,630
I beg you, please let Bo go.

27
00:04:13,430 --> 00:04:14,280
It's my fault.

28
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:15,780
It's all my fault.

29
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:18,050
Let him know

30
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,070
who truly calls the shots

31
00:04:20,070 --> 00:04:21,339
in Great Xia!

32
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:22,620
No!

33
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,430
Weren't you asking to be beaten?

34
00:04:25,430 --> 00:04:26,560
Don't hit her!

35
00:04:27,030 --> 00:04:27,590
Mother!

36
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,000
Mother!

37
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,270
Mother!

38
00:05:34,490 --> 00:05:38,550
[Peiyang]

39
00:05:38,670 --> 00:05:38,970
You.

40
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:41,190
Those men are wearing
the border army's armor.

41
00:05:41,190 --> 00:05:41,720
It seems

42
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:44,040
they've taken full control of
Peiyang City.

43
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:44,510
Show yours.

44
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:45,480
But if they've occupied the city,

45
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,950
-You may go.
-why would they reopen the gates

46
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:48,360
and allow the common people come and go?

47
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,830
His Majesty said in his letter

48
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:52,090
that he left reinforcements in Peiyang.

49
00:05:52,190 --> 00:05:53,480
We must enter the city at once...

50
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,210
Turn around.

51
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,159
And find them.

52
00:05:56,070 --> 00:05:57,830
Only then will we have a chance
to rescue His Majesty.

53
00:05:57,830 --> 00:05:59,830
But the border army has
tens of thousands of troops.

54
00:05:59,830 --> 00:06:01,670
If we enter now and get exposed,

55
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:03,750
there will truly be no escape for us.

56
00:06:03,750 --> 00:06:05,120
-Nothing ventured,
-You, come here.

57
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,050
nothing gained.

58
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:09,100
This is our only option right now.

59
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:11,040
It seems these guards...

60
00:06:11,190 --> 00:06:11,480
You may enter.

61
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,800
Are only checking luggage.

62
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:13,130
Go on.

63
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:15,680
They don't seem to be looking for anyone.

64
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,310
Your Highness,

65
00:06:16,310 --> 00:06:17,370
it's still unwise.

66
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:19,480
Did His Majesty leave any token?

67
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:21,120
How about letting us enter the city
to search first?

68
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:24,780
We'll come back to fetch Your Highness
once the news is confirmed.

69
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:26,190
Token...

70
00:06:26,630 --> 00:06:27,140
Yours.

71
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:28,410
Move along.

72
00:06:35,390 --> 00:06:37,720
Thank you for bringing us all the way
to Peiyang.

73
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,920
I've had them prepare some travel expenses
for you.

74
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,780
Your Highness.

75
00:06:42,980 --> 00:06:45,120
There's no need for you
to follow us any further.

76
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,650
Find a place to settle down.

77
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,130
Let's go.

78
00:06:51,070 --> 00:06:53,310
There's no reason for you guys
to risk your lives for me.

79
00:06:53,310 --> 00:06:55,040
Let's enter the city together.

80
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:05,680
[Peiyang]

81
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:02,690
Go on.

82
00:07:04,860 --> 00:07:05,660
You may enter.

83
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:07,190
Let's go.

84
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:08,770
Go ahead.

85
00:07:09,630 --> 00:07:10,490
You. Come here.

86
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,680
-Stop.
-What's inside?

87
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,140
Hold on.

88
00:07:20,330 --> 00:07:20,930
Come here.

89
00:07:20,950 --> 00:07:21,480
Officer.

90
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:24,000
-We're here for medical treatment.
-Go on in.

91
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,040
Take out your things for inspection.

92
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,410
Follow me, all of you.

93
00:07:35,970 --> 00:07:39,390
[Prefect's Mansion]

94
00:07:42,170 --> 00:07:44,950
[Prefect's Mansion]

95
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,130
General Lin, they're here.

96
00:07:57,630 --> 00:07:58,120
Wanyin.

97
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,360
Bai?

98
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,100
Smells so good!

99
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:07,800
Put out another set of tableware,
will you?

100
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,680
Don't be stingy.

101
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,510
You are the Emperor now.

102
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:11,370
What's one more set of tableware?

103
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:13,510
Last night when I observed the stars,

104
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:14,680
I noticed that the five stars
were about to align.

105
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,250
So?

106
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:16,750
Don't take this lightly.

107
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:18,360
Master's divinations are always accurate,

108
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:20,720
and he asked me to pass along
one more thing:

109
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,190
your meeting with each other

110
00:08:22,190 --> 00:08:23,920
may not be a blessing after all.

111
00:08:27,950 --> 00:08:28,410
It's me.

112
00:08:32,710 --> 00:08:33,640
Come in, please.

113
00:08:38,179 --> 00:08:39,390
Moving around the camp,

114
00:08:39,390 --> 00:08:41,789
men's clothing is indeed more convenient.

115
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,909
Here's the freshly brewed medicine.

116
00:08:43,909 --> 00:08:45,110
It's cooled down now.

117
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:49,360
Thank you, General Lin.

118
00:08:59,120 --> 00:08:59,720
Actually,

119
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,980
I still prefer you call me Bai.

120
00:09:03,430 --> 00:09:04,830
So who are you really, Bai

121
00:09:05,510 --> 00:09:06,440
or Lin Xuanying?

122
00:09:07,030 --> 00:09:08,030
I'm Lin Xuanying.

123
00:09:12,750 --> 00:09:15,030
I originally thought
you killed Lin Xuanying

124
00:09:15,030 --> 00:09:16,630
and were impersonating him.

125
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:19,090
But after thinking it through,

126
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:21,530
even though you've grown a beard,

127
00:09:21,870 --> 00:09:23,470
how could there be two people

128
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:25,800
who look exactly the same in this world?

129
00:09:26,420 --> 00:09:28,350
I was born with a lock of white hair.

130
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,240
Bai

131
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:32,090
is the nickname Master gave me.

132
00:09:32,150 --> 00:09:34,000
But you had just finished
your apprenticeship.

133
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:36,360
How did you become
a Deputy General so quickly?

134
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:36,960
Well...

135
00:09:41,870 --> 00:09:45,000
Because you hadn't just finished
your apprenticeship.

136
00:09:50,870 --> 00:09:51,870
Our first meeting

137
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:56,080
wasn't actually your first meeting
with His Majesty, was it?

138
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,750
How long have you two known each other?

139
00:09:57,750 --> 00:09:59,280
This involves some secrets

140
00:10:00,790 --> 00:10:02,630
I can't speak of.

141
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,100
If you are referring to

142
00:10:08,270 --> 00:10:10,470
His Majesty's past from another world,

143
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:14,910
he wrote me a letter

144
00:10:16,070 --> 00:10:17,400
and told me everything.

145
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:24,480
He tried every way to keep it from you

146
00:10:24,870 --> 00:10:26,870
because he was worried
it would scare you away.

147
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:27,520
Years ago,

148
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:30,670
my master, the Nameless,
cast a heavenly divination

149
00:10:30,670 --> 00:10:31,730
and predicted that

150
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,500
the arrival of a child from another world

151
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:36,330
would change the state's fate.

152
00:10:37,690 --> 00:10:40,120
He had intended to personally
step in to assist,

153
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:41,250
but that divination

154
00:10:41,730 --> 00:10:43,530
revealed the workings of heaven

155
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,700
and severely drained his energy.

156
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:47,970
He could only stay home to recuperate,

157
00:10:48,510 --> 00:10:51,510
so he sent me out after graduating
to find His Majesty.

158
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:53,460
But after I arrived at the palace,

159
00:10:53,790 --> 00:10:54,720
His Majesty said

160
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:57,390
he had another purpose for me to serve.

161
00:10:57,390 --> 00:10:59,190
I've secretly trained a group of

162
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,700
secret guards loyal to me.

163
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:03,840
There's not much point in you
staying by my side to protect me.

164
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:05,170
What do you need me to do?

165
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:11,650
Without military power,
I have no trump card.

166
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:13,840
No matter how I maneuver,

167
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:17,290
I can't overthrow
my enemies in the court.

168
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:18,790
So,

169
00:11:21,790 --> 00:11:24,050
have you thought about joining the army?

170
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:26,810
After that, I infiltrated the Right Army.

171
00:11:27,910 --> 00:11:28,410
Indeed.

172
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,000
The Right Army

173
00:11:31,630 --> 00:11:34,230
is the furthest from
Prince Duan's influence.

174
00:11:35,270 --> 00:11:37,120
Your small maneuvers in there

175
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,690
would be hard to detect.

176
00:11:39,030 --> 00:11:40,720
It was also thanks to the fact that

177
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:41,690
General You

178
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:42,840
is a fool.

179
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,910
As the commander of the Right Army,

180
00:11:44,910 --> 00:11:46,510
General You doesn't have a shred of
a true general's bearing.

181
00:11:46,510 --> 00:11:48,320
I don't expect him
to accomplish anything significant.

182
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,720
But with him in that post,

183
00:11:50,270 --> 00:11:51,400
I can't command him,

184
00:11:51,790 --> 00:11:52,920
nor can Prince Duan.

185
00:11:53,660 --> 00:11:55,750
His Majesty and I worked,
one in the open and one in the shadows,

186
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:57,570
so we could undermine him
right under the noses

187
00:11:57,570 --> 00:11:58,700
of all the factions.

188
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:00,210
Now, the Right Army

189
00:12:00,950 --> 00:12:02,610
basically follows my orders.

190
00:12:04,790 --> 00:12:05,650
Your Highness.

191
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:07,620
You can trust me.

192
00:12:07,990 --> 00:12:09,250
I gave you that hairpin

193
00:12:10,270 --> 00:12:11,800
for you to wear in your hair,

194
00:12:13,930 --> 00:12:15,190
not to hold in your hand

195
00:12:16,950 --> 00:12:18,610
as a weapon for self-defense.

196
00:12:27,630 --> 00:12:28,230
I'm sorry,

197
00:12:28,670 --> 00:12:29,110
Bai.

198
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:31,650
So much has happened along the way,

199
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:34,150
and meeting you in Peiyang

200
00:12:34,150 --> 00:12:35,150
was just too easy,

201
00:12:35,550 --> 00:12:36,670
so I couldn't help but be suspicious.

202
00:12:36,670 --> 00:12:37,470
I understand.

203
00:12:37,910 --> 00:12:39,750
That's why, starting from Peiyang,

204
00:12:39,750 --> 00:12:41,010
I've had my trusted men

205
00:12:41,530 --> 00:12:42,720
take shifts at the city gates
day and night,

206
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:44,120
patrolling constantly.

207
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,600
I was worried
you might disguise yourself,

208
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:47,130
so I specifically told them

209
00:12:47,390 --> 00:12:49,720
to look out for a skylark-shaped hairpin.

210
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:51,630
Thank you,

211
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:52,600
Bai.

212
00:13:07,270 --> 00:13:08,030
Drag him

213
00:13:09,150 --> 00:13:10,540
away.

214
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:12,390
Your Highness, please spare my life!

215
00:13:12,390 --> 00:13:14,190
Your Highness, please spare me!

216
00:13:14,750 --> 00:13:15,790
Your Highness, please spare me!

217
00:13:15,790 --> 00:13:16,600
Your Highness!

218
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,800
Please spare my life!

219
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:27,200
Imperial Physician Zhang,

220
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,790
how is

221
00:13:31,030 --> 00:13:32,150
my leg?

222
00:13:36,150 --> 00:13:38,390
Your Highness is blessed with
extraordinary fortune.

223
00:13:38,390 --> 00:13:39,130
Given time,

224
00:13:39,790 --> 00:13:40,550
it'll surely heal...

225
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:41,800
I want the truth!

226
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:45,640
We will do our utmost to treat it.

227
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:47,980
-We will do our best.
-We will do our best.

228
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,060
Your Highness,

229
00:13:49,390 --> 00:13:50,520
the wound on your leg

230
00:13:50,670 --> 00:13:52,130
is highly prone to causing

231
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,030
sepsis.

232
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,950
Amputation is needed immediately

233
00:13:55,950 --> 00:13:57,200
to save your life.

234
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,150
Very well.

235
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:07,180
None of you could tell!

236
00:14:09,670 --> 00:14:10,270
Guards.

237
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:13,480
Except for him,

238
00:14:14,270 --> 00:14:15,330
drag the rest away.

239
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,320
-Your Highness!
-Your Highness! Your Highness!

240
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,440
-Your Highness, please wait.
-Your Highness!

241
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:20,300
-Your Highness!
-Your Highness.

242
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:20,720
Your Highness,

243
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:23,120
they simply didn't dare
tell you the truth.

244
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:28,160
A bunch of useless trash.

245
00:14:29,510 --> 00:14:30,830
Get lost.

246
00:14:31,450 --> 00:14:33,090
-Thank you, Your Highness.
-Thank you, Your Highness.

247
00:14:33,090 --> 00:14:36,150
-Thank you, Your Highness.
-Thank you, Your Highness.

248
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:46,080
What is

249
00:14:47,670 --> 00:14:48,670
your name?

250
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:51,030
I am

251
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:52,880
Xiao Tiancai.

252
00:14:54,590 --> 00:14:55,450
Your Highness,

253
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:56,550
he is that Physician Xiao

254
00:14:56,550 --> 00:14:59,210
who has been
keeping the Empress Dowager alive.

255
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:07,960
You said you could treat my leg.

256
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:09,790
As I said,

257
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:13,010
amputation is the only way

258
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:14,790
to save your life.

259
00:15:15,750 --> 00:15:17,510
Are you absolutely certain?

260
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:21,050
Even the greatest doctor alive

261
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:23,720
wouldn't dare guarantee
absolute certainty.

262
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:24,780
But as a physician,

263
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:27,360
I'll surely give it my utmost effort

264
00:15:27,670 --> 00:15:28,530
to heal the sick

265
00:15:28,550 --> 00:15:29,410
and save lives.

266
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:34,240
Alright.

267
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:36,800
You may leave for now.

268
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:39,670
I'll think about it.

269
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:45,960
In fact, as early as
the beginning of last year,

270
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:47,760
we were already fully prepared.

271
00:15:47,870 --> 00:15:48,480
We planned

272
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:50,150
to purge the entire Right Army

273
00:15:50,150 --> 00:15:51,350
and then declare war.

274
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:54,450
Although victory wasn't guaranteed,

275
00:15:54,910 --> 00:15:57,390
by striking unexpectedly
and catching them off guard,

276
00:15:57,390 --> 00:15:58,250
even if we died,

277
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:02,460
we could take the Empress Dowager
and Prince Duan down with us.

278
00:16:03,910 --> 00:16:05,270
Those were His Majesty's exact words.

279
00:16:05,270 --> 00:16:06,150
But just then,

280
00:16:08,150 --> 00:16:08,950
you appeared.

281
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:14,910
What's the point of laying out
such a grand scheme

282
00:16:14,910 --> 00:16:16,460
and taking so many detours?

283
00:16:16,670 --> 00:16:18,040
If we weren't going to attack directly,

284
00:16:18,040 --> 00:16:19,750
why send me to the Right Army
in the first place?

285
00:16:19,750 --> 00:16:20,750
Careful planning

286
00:16:22,910 --> 00:16:24,670
is to minimize casualties.

287
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:27,320
But the situation is changing rapidly.

288
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:28,790
If we keep dragging this out,

289
00:16:28,790 --> 00:16:31,520
even our last chance of victory
might evaporate.

290
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:33,200
I just don't understand—

291
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:35,000
why should you listen to a woman?

292
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:36,130
Because in her eyes,

293
00:16:37,270 --> 00:16:39,200
whether it's peddlers and porters

294
00:16:39,390 --> 00:16:40,920
or commoners and peasants—

295
00:16:41,270 --> 00:16:42,270
every single life

296
00:16:43,910 --> 00:16:44,870
is precious.

297
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:48,930
So that day,

298
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:49,910
in the woods, you...

299
00:16:49,910 --> 00:16:50,240
Yes.

300
00:16:50,870 --> 00:16:51,930
I just wanted to see

301
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:53,870
what kind of woman

302
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:56,960
could actually change His Majesty.

303
00:17:06,750 --> 00:17:08,020
So in your eyes,

304
00:17:08,480 --> 00:17:10,540
I'm nothing more than a tiny skylark.

305
00:17:11,030 --> 00:17:12,069
I misjudged you.

306
00:17:13,589 --> 00:17:14,920
But His Majesty didn't.

307
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:17,180
The world isn't just for roaming freely.

308
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:19,700
She has her own ambitions.

309
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:22,000
You only see her as a little bird

310
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:23,400
that needs to be set free,

311
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:24,680
but you fail to see

312
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:27,839
how upright and noble she is—

313
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:29,980
radiant as the sun,

314
00:17:30,790 --> 00:17:32,650
able to light up the vast blue sky.

315
00:17:36,310 --> 00:17:37,000
By the way,

316
00:17:38,030 --> 00:17:39,760
do you have news of His Majesty?

317
00:17:40,020 --> 00:17:41,080
We had agreed that

318
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,480
if he managed to escape alive,

319
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:45,080
we'd rendezvous in Peiyang.

320
00:17:45,150 --> 00:17:47,240
So I hurried here to
take control of the place,

321
00:17:47,240 --> 00:17:48,570
just to wait for you two.

322
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:49,310
But

323
00:17:50,960 --> 00:17:51,960
only you arrived.

324
00:17:52,440 --> 00:17:53,460
What about Prince Duan?

325
00:17:53,460 --> 00:17:54,460
Is there any news?

326
00:17:54,720 --> 00:17:56,070
That scoundrel Prince Duan

327
00:17:56,070 --> 00:17:57,720
claims His Majesty was suddenly
struck with a serious illness

328
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:59,070
and is recuperating inside the palace,

329
00:17:59,070 --> 00:18:00,790
but whether it's true or not is unknown.

330
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:02,120
Is the source reliable?

331
00:18:03,540 --> 00:18:05,590
The capital is sealed tight right now.

332
00:18:05,590 --> 00:18:06,320
My spies will

333
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:07,820
need more time.

334
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:13,200
Then...

335
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:14,060
Your Highness.

336
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:15,220
It's getting late.

337
00:18:16,350 --> 00:18:17,750
You should get some rest.

338
00:18:21,110 --> 00:18:22,160
I will go and settle

339
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:23,960
the people you brought with you.

340
00:18:24,920 --> 00:18:26,200
Early tomorrow morning,

341
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:27,860
I'll show you something nice.

342
00:18:29,240 --> 00:18:30,100
I take my leave.

343
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:39,620
Xiahou Dan.

344
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:42,240
I've found the reinforcements.

345
00:18:44,350 --> 00:18:47,810
If you've truly been placed
under house arrest by Prince Duan,

346
00:18:50,270 --> 00:18:50,930
wait for me.

347
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:55,020
I'll definitely come to save you.

348
00:19:00,550 --> 00:19:01,210
Gentlemen.

349
00:19:01,550 --> 00:19:02,920
We've endured humiliation for so long

350
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:04,380
and finally gained power,

351
00:19:04,550 --> 00:19:07,030
so why are you sighing?

352
00:19:07,110 --> 00:19:07,990
Gained power?

353
00:19:08,590 --> 00:19:09,790
Throughout history,

354
00:19:10,070 --> 00:19:11,410
have you ever seen

355
00:19:11,440 --> 00:19:13,520
an emperor sitting in a wheelchair?

356
00:19:14,030 --> 00:19:16,090
So His Highness's leg can't be saved?

357
00:19:17,070 --> 00:19:18,350
Don't ask.

358
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:20,720
With the Empress Dowager
being assassinated and the Crown Prince

359
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:23,270
rebelling on one side, and the Emperor
gravely injured and the Empress in exile

360
00:19:23,270 --> 00:19:25,480
on the other—
after such chaos in the court,

361
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:27,740
what's the point of holding court at all?

362
00:19:27,750 --> 00:19:29,070
We nearly lost our lives

363
00:19:29,070 --> 00:19:30,900
on Mount Bei.

364
00:19:31,830 --> 00:19:34,240
What a mess
the Imperial Observatory has made.

365
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:35,880
They claimed it was an auspicious place,

366
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:36,790
but in my opinion,

367
00:19:36,790 --> 00:19:38,370
it was complete nonsense.

368
00:19:42,790 --> 00:19:43,550
This is bad.

369
00:19:43,550 --> 00:19:44,610
This is really bad.

370
00:19:45,030 --> 00:19:46,000
Prince Duan has surrounded
His Majesty's chambers

371
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:47,070
as tight as a drum.

372
00:19:47,350 --> 00:19:48,200
I asked around everywhere

373
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:49,970
but couldn't get
the slightest bit of news.

374
00:19:49,970 --> 00:19:50,430
This...

375
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:52,000
We must not lose our composure.

376
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:53,720
If His Majesty had been killed,

377
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:56,000
Prince Duan would have brought out
the Crown Prince to act as regent.

378
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:57,420
There would be no need to
make such a commotion.

379
00:19:57,420 --> 00:19:58,720
With traitors and rebels in power,

380
00:19:58,720 --> 00:20:00,720
how can we sit idly by and do nothing?

381
00:20:02,070 --> 00:20:04,200
Even if we have to risk our lives today,

382
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:05,670
we must force Prince Duan

383
00:20:05,830 --> 00:20:07,760
to let us see His Majesty in person.

384
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:19,070
My lords, silence please!

385
00:20:28,670 --> 00:20:30,600
Regarding the Mount Bei incident,

386
00:20:31,790 --> 00:20:33,850
His Majesty suffered a severe shock.

387
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:37,170
His head ailment has flared up,
and he needs rest.

388
00:20:37,200 --> 00:20:38,860
Therefore, the court affairs

389
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:40,850
will be temporarily handled by me.

390
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:42,070
This...

391
00:20:42,070 --> 00:20:42,640
This...

392
00:20:44,550 --> 00:20:46,160
In these extraordinary times,

393
00:20:46,160 --> 00:20:48,440
I hope you all will cooperate fully

394
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:51,260
to help His Majesty through this crisis.

395
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:03,400
Gentlemen,

396
00:21:05,070 --> 00:21:06,930
do any of you have any objections?

397
00:21:38,680 --> 00:21:41,010
I have something to report, Your Majesty.

398
00:21:41,480 --> 00:21:42,740
Please speak, Lord Wu.

399
00:21:42,870 --> 00:21:43,980
How dare you!

400
00:21:47,830 --> 00:21:48,490
Wu Jiadong,

401
00:21:49,310 --> 00:21:51,160
as a high-ranking official
of the third rank,

402
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:52,070
with His Majesty absent,

403
00:21:52,070 --> 00:21:54,200
who were you addressing as "Your Majesty"?

404
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:54,640
No, I...

405
00:21:54,640 --> 00:21:56,440
-This...
-Do you intend to put
His Highness Prince Duan

406
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:58,240
in a position of treason and rebellion?

407
00:21:58,240 --> 00:21:59,000
This... This is...

408
00:21:59,000 --> 00:21:59,400
You...

409
00:22:00,550 --> 00:22:02,070
I misspoke in the heat of the moment.

410
00:22:02,070 --> 00:22:04,800
Please forgive me,
Your Highness Prince Duan.

411
00:22:08,270 --> 00:22:10,470
Lord Wu simply made a slip of the tongue.

412
00:22:11,030 --> 00:22:12,230
Lord Li, Mr. Li Yunxi,

413
00:22:13,240 --> 00:22:15,240
there's no need for such hostility.

414
00:22:16,750 --> 00:22:17,310
We

415
00:22:18,480 --> 00:22:20,080
live on His Majesty's salary

416
00:22:20,550 --> 00:22:22,280
and serve His Majesty loyally.

417
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:24,680
If we disregard propriety and the law,

418
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:27,780
then we're unworthy of
being His Majesty's ministers.

419
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:30,370
Then how do you intend to act
as a minister?

420
00:22:30,510 --> 00:22:31,200
I

421
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:35,460
would like to ask
Your Highness Prince Duan a question:

422
00:22:36,750 --> 00:22:37,770
when

423
00:22:38,740 --> 00:22:41,000
can we have an audience with His Majesty?

424
00:22:48,510 --> 00:22:49,760
I've already said it.

425
00:22:50,270 --> 00:22:51,930
His Majesty is critically ill

426
00:22:52,720 --> 00:22:54,270
and needs to rest.

427
00:22:54,550 --> 00:22:56,180
I prefer to see it for myself.

428
00:22:56,440 --> 00:22:57,840
Lord Li, are you implying

429
00:22:58,930 --> 00:23:00,550
that I'm lying?

430
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:02,640
If there were an imperial decree as proof,

431
00:23:02,640 --> 00:23:03,300
I naturally

432
00:23:03,830 --> 00:23:05,230
would have no objection.

433
00:23:07,920 --> 00:23:10,510
But now, Your Highness Prince Duan
has nothing to show

434
00:23:10,510 --> 00:23:11,550
yet wishes to act as regent.

435
00:23:11,550 --> 00:23:12,250
May I ask—

436
00:23:12,960 --> 00:23:14,230
where is His Majesty,

437
00:23:14,270 --> 00:23:15,680
where is the Crown Prince,

438
00:23:15,680 --> 00:23:18,300
and where is the Empress?

439
00:23:29,350 --> 00:23:31,030
Are you asking me about
that demonic empress?

440
00:23:31,030 --> 00:23:33,330
I also wish to catch that culprit.

441
00:23:34,110 --> 00:23:35,040
However, I heard

442
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:37,000
that you, Lord Li,

443
00:23:37,340 --> 00:23:39,870
were highly favored by
that demonic empress.

444
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:41,780
Do you happen to know where she is?

445
00:23:42,510 --> 00:23:43,030
I...

446
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:43,860
I

447
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:45,890
observed the stars last night.

448
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:48,890
The Emperor Star was dim,

449
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:50,680
and the Treasury Star appeared,

450
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:52,790
yet it was also shrouded by dark clouds—

451
00:23:52,790 --> 00:23:54,880
much like the current state of affairs,

452
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:58,210
where things are unclear
as if viewing flowers through fog.

453
00:23:59,070 --> 00:24:01,200
Therefore, what Lord Li meant was that

454
00:24:01,440 --> 00:24:03,350
the Mount Bei incident
is highly suspicious,

455
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:05,480
with many doubts still unresolved, so

456
00:24:05,510 --> 00:24:08,040
it's far too early
to draw a final conclusion.

457
00:24:08,110 --> 00:24:08,510
But...

458
00:24:08,590 --> 00:24:09,400
But

459
00:24:10,750 --> 00:24:12,400
His Highness Prince Duan would never

460
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:15,030
base the guilt of the Empress

461
00:24:15,110 --> 00:24:17,540
solely on the word of a mere assassin.

462
00:24:17,960 --> 00:24:18,490
Of course

463
00:24:18,510 --> 00:24:21,240
we'll need to wait for His Majesty
to wake up, right?

464
00:24:21,240 --> 00:24:21,900
Lord Yang.

465
00:24:22,240 --> 00:24:24,110
You are mistaken, Lord Yang.

466
00:24:24,590 --> 00:24:26,550
Lord Li's request to see His Majesty

467
00:24:26,550 --> 00:24:29,400
concerns matters of state
handled by all departments.

468
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:31,600
What does that have to do with the harem?

469
00:24:31,830 --> 00:24:33,750
Especially for our Ministry of Revenue—

470
00:24:33,750 --> 00:24:35,110
we have no interest

471
00:24:35,170 --> 00:24:36,590
in His Majesty's private affairs.

472
00:24:36,590 --> 00:24:37,400
Am I right,

473
00:24:38,350 --> 00:24:39,390
Lord Chen?

474
00:24:45,590 --> 00:24:48,070
The Ministry of Revenue
has many pressing matters

475
00:24:48,070 --> 00:24:49,200
that indeed require

476
00:24:49,510 --> 00:24:50,680
an audience with His Majesty

477
00:24:50,680 --> 00:24:51,810
as soon as possible.

478
00:24:53,240 --> 00:24:54,140
Exactly.

479
00:24:54,510 --> 00:24:57,640
The Mount Bei incident caused the deaths
and injuries of many court ministers.

480
00:24:57,640 --> 00:25:00,230
Personnel changes cannot be enacted

481
00:25:00,550 --> 00:25:02,830
without His Majesty's seal.

482
00:25:03,590 --> 00:25:05,250
The Empress Dowager's coffin

483
00:25:05,270 --> 00:25:07,000
hasn't been interred, either.

484
00:25:07,440 --> 00:25:09,480
The mausoleum construction
is not yet finished.

485
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:10,960
I do wish to proceed with the burial,

486
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:12,190
but how could I?

487
00:25:12,880 --> 00:25:14,340
-That's right.
-Exactly.

488
00:25:17,110 --> 00:25:17,590
Exactly.

489
00:25:17,590 --> 00:25:18,400
Indeed.

490
00:25:25,680 --> 00:25:26,920
Silence!

491
00:25:29,340 --> 00:25:31,600
Once His Majesty has recovered a little,

492
00:25:33,890 --> 00:25:35,690
he'll naturally summon you all.

493
00:25:46,750 --> 00:25:47,830
And when will that be?

494
00:25:47,830 --> 00:25:48,440
When?

495
00:25:48,880 --> 00:25:50,070
Your Highness Prince Duan,

496
00:25:50,070 --> 00:25:51,070
when will that be!

497
00:26:02,070 --> 00:26:05,270
Nine Heavens Mystical Fire
Repeating Sleeve Crossbows.

498
00:26:06,180 --> 00:26:07,240
How many do we have?

499
00:26:07,510 --> 00:26:08,370
Your Highness,

500
00:26:08,920 --> 00:26:10,520
there are thousands of them,

501
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:12,740
plus dozens of crates of ammunition.

502
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:19,630
The blueprints

503
00:26:19,630 --> 00:26:21,030
were sent by His Majesty.

504
00:26:21,270 --> 00:26:22,860
To prevent them from being intercepted
along the way,

505
00:26:22,860 --> 00:26:24,680
the crossbows were
dismantled into countless components

506
00:26:24,680 --> 00:26:26,350
and delivered in over 10 shipments.

507
00:26:26,350 --> 00:26:28,410
We then enlisted the best craftsmen,

508
00:26:28,480 --> 00:26:30,080
and after several failures,

509
00:26:30,440 --> 00:26:32,570
we finally put together the first one.

510
00:26:33,110 --> 00:26:34,440
These sleeve crossbows

511
00:26:34,920 --> 00:26:36,270
were extremely difficult to obtain,

512
00:26:36,270 --> 00:26:38,030
but their combat power is unparalleled.

513
00:26:38,030 --> 00:26:38,480
Even

514
00:26:39,510 --> 00:26:42,480
against tens of thousands of troops
of the other two armies,

515
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:44,240
they'll crush them like dry weeds,

516
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:46,240
without shedding a drop of our own blood.

517
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:47,840
Thank you for your hard work.

518
00:26:52,790 --> 00:26:53,330
Today,

519
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:55,400
our army marches.

520
00:26:56,070 --> 00:26:58,000
At the highlands 500 li from the capital,

521
00:26:58,000 --> 00:26:59,590
we can intercept
the Left and Central Armies.

522
00:26:59,590 --> 00:26:59,880
We

523
00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:02,240
have endured in silence for years,

524
00:27:02,240 --> 00:27:03,570
sleeping on our spears,

525
00:27:04,510 --> 00:27:06,880
just waiting for today—
the moment of certain victory.

526
00:27:06,880 --> 00:27:08,790
Prince Duan conspires in rebellion

527
00:27:08,790 --> 00:27:10,190
and acts as a pawn of evil.

528
00:27:11,960 --> 00:27:13,960
Just give the order, Your Highness,

529
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:14,800
and we will

530
00:27:15,870 --> 00:27:17,830
execute him for the sake of the realm.

531
00:27:17,830 --> 00:27:19,890
Execute him for the sake of the realm!

532
00:27:23,350 --> 00:27:24,080
General Lin.

533
00:27:24,550 --> 00:27:26,150
Let's have a word in private.

534
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,920
His Majesty's whereabouts
are still unknown.

535
00:27:31,920 --> 00:27:33,050
If we attack rashly,

536
00:27:33,550 --> 00:27:35,550
and he really is in Prince Duan's hands,

537
00:27:35,550 --> 00:27:36,680
what will we do then?

538
00:27:37,790 --> 00:27:39,450
This is the final secret edict

539
00:27:39,510 --> 00:27:41,640
His Majesty gave me before I departed.

540
00:27:43,560 --> 00:27:44,780
[Order Crown Prince to succeed the throne;
confer Yu Wanyin as Empress Dowager]

541
00:27:44,800 --> 00:27:46,480
[Promote Li Yunxi and Yang Duojie
to assist in managing state affairs]

542
00:27:46,500 --> 00:27:47,650
[Traitor Xiahou Bo shall be executed
without hesitation. Put the realm first]

543
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:48,140
He wants the Crown Prince
to succeed the throne

544
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:48,740
[at all times; do not concern yourselves
with my life or death]

545
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:51,310
and me to become the Empress Dowager?

546
00:27:51,310 --> 00:27:52,170
Only in this way

547
00:27:52,790 --> 00:27:55,440
can you justifiably
hold control over the court.

548
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:56,900
He's also left behind many

549
00:27:57,310 --> 00:27:58,680
to assist in governing state affairs.

550
00:27:58,680 --> 00:28:01,240
Traitor Xiahou Bo shall be executed
without hesitation.

551
00:28:01,240 --> 00:28:03,040
Put the realm first at all times;

552
00:28:03,310 --> 00:28:05,970
do not concern yourselves with
my life or death.

553
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:06,720
He knew

554
00:28:07,510 --> 00:28:09,170
he didn't have much time left.

555
00:28:09,270 --> 00:28:11,590
He didn't want to become a burden
to you in his final moments,

556
00:28:11,590 --> 00:28:13,920
nor did he wish to be humiliated
in the enemy camp.

557
00:28:13,920 --> 00:28:16,030
If, by misfortune, he were captured
by Prince Duan,

558
00:28:16,030 --> 00:28:18,630
he would find a way to
perish together with him.

559
00:28:18,750 --> 00:28:20,590
And if even that were impossible,

560
00:28:20,590 --> 00:28:21,250
he would...

561
00:28:24,070 --> 00:28:25,000
Take his own life.

562
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:25,750
So you just

563
00:28:25,750 --> 00:28:27,240
gave up on him as a matter of course?

564
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:28,040
Of course not!

565
00:28:28,750 --> 00:28:30,400
I've seized every possible chance
to look for him.

566
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:32,150
Then find him first
before mobilizing the troops!

567
00:28:32,150 --> 00:28:33,920
You know there isn't enough time.

568
00:28:33,920 --> 00:28:36,640
The rebels are marching toward
the capital day and night.

569
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:38,160
Prince Duan is scouring everywhere
for you,

570
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:40,360
and he'll soon trace you to my location.

571
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:42,640
But if Xiahou Dan's safety
cannot be guaranteed,

572
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:44,190
none of this means anything.

573
00:28:44,190 --> 00:28:45,480
His Majesty's final secret edict

574
00:28:45,480 --> 00:28:46,830
was precisely to force us
to consider the bigger picture

575
00:28:46,830 --> 00:28:48,090
and act without delay.

576
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:49,000
Lin Xuanying.

577
00:28:50,590 --> 00:28:52,350
Why are you so eager
to mobilize the troops?

578
00:28:52,350 --> 00:28:54,080
What exactly are you planning?

579
00:28:56,010 --> 00:28:57,670
Whether you believe me or not,

580
00:28:58,470 --> 00:29:00,930
I have absolutely no interest in
any of this.

581
00:29:01,190 --> 00:29:02,270
I only came here

582
00:29:02,830 --> 00:29:05,160
on Master's orders to assist His Majesty,

583
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:07,200
and His Majesty asked me to
take orders from you.

584
00:29:07,200 --> 00:29:07,930
Then my order

585
00:29:08,030 --> 00:29:09,960
is to save him at all costs.

586
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:12,970
General.

587
00:29:16,510 --> 00:29:17,040
General,

588
00:29:17,410 --> 00:29:19,110
shall we distribute these sleeve crossbows

589
00:29:19,110 --> 00:29:20,000
to the army

590
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:21,720
and issue orders to prepare for battle?

591
00:29:21,720 --> 00:29:24,380
Deputy General of the Right Army,
Lin Xuanying!

592
00:29:29,410 --> 00:29:29,880
Yes.

593
00:29:30,760 --> 00:29:32,690
His Majesty ordered you to obey me,

594
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:34,000
didn't he?

595
00:29:36,380 --> 00:29:36,750
Yes.

596
00:29:37,010 --> 00:29:38,520
Then I hereby order you

597
00:29:39,700 --> 00:29:41,360
to discard this secret edict.

598
00:29:42,590 --> 00:29:43,720
From this moment on,

599
00:29:45,510 --> 00:29:46,110
you do

600
00:29:47,830 --> 00:29:48,380
as I say.

601
00:30:05,110 --> 00:30:05,870
My lords.

602
00:30:10,270 --> 00:30:10,800
Lord Li.

603
00:30:21,650 --> 00:30:22,320
My lords,

604
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:24,730
it is freezing out here.

605
00:30:25,110 --> 00:30:25,510
Please

606
00:30:26,310 --> 00:30:27,530
go back for now.

607
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:28,880
Eunuch An.

608
00:30:30,480 --> 00:30:31,370
His Majesty

609
00:30:32,310 --> 00:30:33,910
has always treated you well.

610
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:36,170
Why do you now

611
00:30:37,270 --> 00:30:39,160
only take orders from Prince Duan?

612
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:40,870
Besides, we are kneeling here

613
00:30:41,240 --> 00:30:42,920
only to pray for His Majesty.

614
00:30:44,720 --> 00:30:46,050
Why is that not allowed?

615
00:30:46,680 --> 00:30:48,200
We will not leave today

616
00:30:48,790 --> 00:30:50,190
until we see His Majesty.

617
00:30:52,030 --> 00:30:52,630
Lord Chen.

618
00:30:55,980 --> 00:30:57,380
That's right, Eunuch An.

619
00:30:57,720 --> 00:30:58,790
Didn't we make it clear

620
00:30:58,790 --> 00:31:00,090
in the court?

621
00:31:00,440 --> 00:31:02,030
The state affairs are complicated

622
00:31:02,030 --> 00:31:03,210
and cannot wait.

623
00:31:03,510 --> 00:31:06,790
We beg to see His Majesty!

624
00:31:12,510 --> 00:31:13,070
My lords,

625
00:31:14,350 --> 00:31:15,610
please heed my advice.

626
00:31:17,160 --> 00:31:18,790
Right now, the last thing
His Majesty wants to see

627
00:31:18,790 --> 00:31:20,750
is a scene like this.

628
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:23,240
As for the complicated state affairs,

629
00:31:23,240 --> 00:31:24,300
please handle them

630
00:31:24,640 --> 00:31:25,770
yourselves for now.

631
00:31:26,510 --> 00:31:27,970
The situation is chaotic.

632
00:31:28,240 --> 00:31:29,200
It would be better

633
00:31:29,200 --> 00:31:30,260
to observe quietly

634
00:31:30,880 --> 00:31:31,940
before acting.

635
00:31:33,270 --> 00:31:35,350
You're all pillars of Great Xia.

636
00:31:37,640 --> 00:31:38,500
At this moment,

637
00:31:39,160 --> 00:31:41,020
besides head-on confrontation,

638
00:31:41,160 --> 00:31:43,820
what's more important is
to protect yourselves

639
00:31:44,310 --> 00:31:46,310
and proceed with careful planning.

640
00:31:46,480 --> 00:31:47,080
Eunuch An,

641
00:31:47,750 --> 00:31:48,960
there's no need to advise us further.

642
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:50,820
We don't speak the same language.

643
00:31:51,110 --> 00:31:51,550
We

644
00:31:52,350 --> 00:31:53,210
will not leave.

645
00:31:55,350 --> 00:31:55,960
Eunuch An!

646
00:31:56,690 --> 00:31:57,290
Eunuch An!

647
00:31:58,590 --> 00:31:59,120
Bad news!

648
00:31:59,480 --> 00:32:00,010
Bad news!

649
00:32:00,480 --> 00:32:01,740
His... His Majesty...

650
00:32:04,590 --> 00:32:05,450
His Majesty...

651
00:32:06,550 --> 00:32:09,970
His Majesty has passed away!

652
00:32:10,640 --> 00:32:12,510
Your Majesty.

653
00:32:17,550 --> 00:32:19,640
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

654
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:22,800
Your Majesty.

655
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:27,830
Your Majesty!

656
00:32:33,920 --> 00:32:35,920
Please rest assured, Your Majesty.

657
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:39,730
I'll take good care of
the young Crown Prince for you.

658
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:43,640
In these troubled times,

659
00:32:45,310 --> 00:32:47,570
our state cannot go a day without a ruler.

660
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:52,200
Let's prepare for the Crown Prince's
enthronement ceremony immediately.

661
00:32:53,640 --> 00:32:54,680
Where are the Yulin Guards?

662
00:32:54,680 --> 00:32:55,210
Present!

663
00:32:57,510 --> 00:33:00,640
Escort the lords back to their residences
to rest for now

664
00:33:00,680 --> 00:33:01,880
and prepare to
observe the mourning period.

665
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:02,160
Yes!

666
00:33:06,640 --> 00:33:07,480
Report!

667
00:33:10,030 --> 00:33:10,560
General,

668
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:11,790
urgent news from the capital!

669
00:33:11,790 --> 00:33:13,200
His Majesty has passed away!

670
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:13,990
Nonsense!

671
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:18,810
Go and verify this news.

672
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:19,560
Go now!

673
00:33:19,750 --> 00:33:20,030
Yes!

674
00:33:24,440 --> 00:33:25,570
Continue the march!

675
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:34,020
Your Highness,

676
00:33:34,440 --> 00:33:35,570
you heard it, right?

677
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:36,680
That's good news.

678
00:33:37,160 --> 00:33:38,020
Your Highness?

679
00:33:39,750 --> 00:33:41,920
If Prince Duan had really captured
His Majesty,

680
00:33:41,920 --> 00:33:43,250
given his personality,

681
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:46,240
there's no way
he would have let His Majesty die.

682
00:33:46,240 --> 00:33:49,110
After all, only a living hostage
is a bargaining chip.

683
00:33:49,110 --> 00:33:50,170
As for His Majesty,

684
00:33:50,550 --> 00:33:52,150
no matter what he said to you,

685
00:33:52,590 --> 00:33:54,160
before confirming my safety,

686
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:55,920
he would never take his own life.

687
00:33:55,920 --> 00:33:58,160
So this news of his death actually proves

688
00:33:58,160 --> 00:34:00,760
that His Majesty is not
in Prince Duan's hands.

689
00:34:01,070 --> 00:34:02,030
It must be so.

690
00:34:02,890 --> 00:34:03,710
Could it be

691
00:34:05,110 --> 00:34:06,350
because of His Majesty's illness...

692
00:34:06,350 --> 00:34:06,860
No.

693
00:34:08,190 --> 00:34:10,250
He said he would never leave me alone.

694
00:34:11,320 --> 00:34:13,550
He absolutely wouldn't break his promise.

695
00:34:13,550 --> 00:34:14,000
Your Highness.

696
00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:14,659
Say no more.

697
00:34:15,710 --> 00:34:17,630
Prince Duan is a master at
manipulating public opinion.

698
00:34:17,630 --> 00:34:18,489
I won't believe

699
00:34:18,960 --> 00:34:20,159
a single word he says.

700
00:34:35,310 --> 00:34:36,960
We'll be encamping here tonight.

701
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:37,760
The conditions are rough.

702
00:34:37,760 --> 00:34:38,110
Your Highness, you...

703
00:34:38,110 --> 00:34:39,030
Don't worry about me.

704
00:34:39,030 --> 00:34:39,920
Focus on

705
00:34:40,360 --> 00:34:41,889
finding His Majesty first.

706
00:34:51,480 --> 00:34:52,940
Didn't I tell you to leave?

707
00:34:53,110 --> 00:34:54,770
How come you followed me here?

708
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:28,960
But I can't let you tag along.

709
00:35:37,530 --> 00:35:39,730
It's not that I can't afford to feed you,

710
00:35:39,760 --> 00:35:40,940
but we are going to war.

711
00:35:40,940 --> 00:35:42,140
It's very dangerous.

712
00:35:42,550 --> 00:35:43,960
You could lose your life.

713
00:36:02,190 --> 00:36:03,710
But you are too young.

714
00:36:05,480 --> 00:36:07,210
I can't use child labor, right?

715
00:36:28,840 --> 00:36:29,840
Are you telling me

716
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:33,210
not to be afraid?

717
00:36:50,440 --> 00:36:50,880
I know.

718
00:36:54,230 --> 00:36:55,110
I'm not afraid.

719
00:36:59,590 --> 00:37:01,050
I'll definitely find him.

720
00:37:57,440 --> 00:37:58,140
Don't go outside.

721
00:37:58,140 --> 00:37:58,920
Wait for me here.
